{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"5f0f763dac","title":"周恩来接见河南省兰考县张钦礼焦守凤谈话纪要","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"ab50c1969c","index":0,"year":1967,"month":7,"day":30,"articleId":"5f0f763dac","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"对话","id":"314ad57c4d","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"刘建勋","id":"3ae36abefb","type":"人物"},{"name":"周恩来","id":"523bb79e8f","type":"人物"},{"name":"戚本禹","id":"57434e107b","type":"人物"},{"name":"周总理","id":"838b5f2c9d","type":"人物"},{"name":"关键人物文稿","id":"c20d333791","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"造反运动和派别斗争","id":"d48f0ea3e8","type":"主题"},{"name":"杨成武","id":"e1397e909a","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"1dc13d8bd3","type":"title","text":"周恩来接见河南省兰考县张钦礼焦守凤谈话纪要","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5f0f763dac","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4f54f35ed8","type":"paragraph","text":"〖时间：一九六七年七月三十夜；地点：人民大会堂安徽厅外边会议室。〗","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5f0f763dac","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"aefb67bbb5","type":"paragraph","text":"（中央首长处理河南问题的第八次汇报会议开始，刘建勋同志热情地向张钦礼同志招手，张钦礼走到刘建勋同志跟前，刘建勋同志让张钦礼同志坐在杨成武同志的席位上。当时杨成武同志不在首长席 ）","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5f0f763dac","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"249cbce9bd","type":"paragraph","text":"刘建勋（关心地）：听说你的手指被打断了。","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5f0f763dac","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"52f389548a","type":"paragraph","text":"张钦礼：是的。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5f0f763dac","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"088c902a22","type":"paragraph","text":"刘建勋（对总理和张钦礼），控诉他！","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5f0f763dac","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"41e40b9488","type":"paragraph","text":"（总理点了点头，张钦礼同志回到原席位上）","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5f0f763dac","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"fe350f38fd","type":"paragraph","text":"（会议中张钦礼同志讲话时，未讲完就被郑大战斗师、中学红卫兵总部插话打断。张坐下。停了一会，总理走到张钦礼同志面前和张亲切握手，随即拉着张的手走到休息室，同坐在一张沙发上。室内有戚本禹，杨成武等同志。这时，刘建勋同志带焦守凤同志进来。）","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5f0f763dac","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"029da3d7f0","type":"paragraph","text":"刘建勋（给首长介绍）：这是焦裕禄同志的女儿焦守凤。","index":8,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5f0f763dac","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"96e3212b4c","type":"paragraph","text":"（总理站起来和焦守凤同志握手，并让她在张钦礼同志旁边坐下。）","index":9,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5f0f763dac","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2f4e4e0860","type":"paragraph","text":"周总理（关切地问张）：你什么时间到北京？","index":10,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5f0f763dac","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"08a001be5b","type":"paragraph","text":"（张因耳朵被打坏，未听见。）","index":11,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5f0f763dac","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"eb95c914c0","type":"paragraph","text":"焦守凤：他的耳朵被打坏了。","index":12,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5f0f763dac","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f1a985dffe","type":"paragraph","text":"周总理：你给他当翻译。","index":13,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5f0f763dac","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"be1c3c809b","type":"paragraph","text":"周总理（问张）：你什么时候被抓起来的？","index":14,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5f0f763dac","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"85cf315ff3","type":"paragraph","text":"张钦礼：2月26日夜4点被抓。","index":15,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5f0f763dac","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"88b1755cb1","type":"paragraph","text":"周总理：他们什么时候将你放出来的。","index":16,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5f0f763dac","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"80b5572836","type":"paragraph","text":"张钦礼：七月二十八日晨三点。七点由解放军同志送我到北京毛主席身边的。","index":17,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5f0f763dac","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"369cfbd991","type":"paragraph","text":"周总理（关切地）：兰考逮捕了多少人？都是什么人？你在那个监狱押着？","index":18,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5f0f763dac","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1eb6d4499a","type":"paragraph","text":"张钦礼：我在兰考监狱押着，兰考监狱押了二百多人；听说杞县、开封、东明等地也押有兰考的人；兰考大概逮捕一千多人，这个数字我不太清楚。因为我被捕和外界隔绝了。","index":19,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5f0f763dac","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5f3b433823","type":"paragraph","text":"周总理：他们抓的都是什么人？","index":20,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5f0f763dac","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d505095a4d","type":"paragraph","text":"张钦礼：有工人、贫下中农、机关干部、红卫兵小将和革命学生。","index":21,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5f0f763dac","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"62fc0f818a","type":"paragraph","text":"周总理（生气地）：在监狱里他们怎样对待你？","index":22,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5f0f763dac","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"603f74abb9","type":"paragraph","text":"张钦礼：脚上带脚镣，手上带手铐，胳膊上绑绳子，绳子捆得很紧，捆得胳膊都出血了。最毒辣的是制造内伤，用折骨残刑。（张钦礼同志一面说着，一面伸出两个被折的指头。周总理无限关怀地抚摸了它。）","index":23,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5f0f763dac","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1afa50be74","type":"paragraph","text":"周总理（对旁边一个工作人员）：你对联络员说，找个医生给他（用手指张）检查治疗。","index":24,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5f0f763dac","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7096ee1223","type":"paragraph","text":"（总理联络员谢××上前问张的住处，并记下来了。）","index":25,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5f0f763dac","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5063269266","type":"paragraph","text":"周总理（气愤地）是谁抓你的？你在监狱里押了多少时间？","index":26,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5f0f763dac","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2b534bc8a6","type":"paragraph","text":"张钦礼：在监狱押了一百五十六天。逮捕我时是开封军分区政委陈久安，副司令员李地山带部队抓的。（周总理记下李地山的姓名）","index":27,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5f0f763dac","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b3d4a490a3","type":"paragraph","text":"周总理：开封军分区有人支持你们吗？","index":28,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5f0f763dac","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1ef52a0b70","type":"paragraph","text":"张钦礼：在提审我时看来，开封军（分）区的杨司令员和徐副司令员是同情我们的，兰考中队中一部分战士是同情我们的。","index":29,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5f0f763dac","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"61f6dbc496","type":"paragraph","text":"周总理：对他们，你们要区别对待。（并嘱咐张钦礼和焦守凤两同志）回去，你们要艰苦奋战。","index":30,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5f0f763dac","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ad55e47311","type":"paragraph","text":"戚本禹：（问焦守凤）你妈妈来了没有？你还和她吵架吗？","index":31,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5f0f763dac","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c0fc23e6f1","type":"paragraph","text":"焦守凤：她回去了，我没跟她吵架。","index":32,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5f0f763dac","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0788efaf81","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：好好作你妈妈和妹妹的工作，她们会明白过来的。","index":33,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5f0f763dac","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"987c41f584","type":"paragraph","text":"焦守凤：我一定照总理指示去做。（接见到此结束）","index":34,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5f0f763dac","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"79ceb01236","type":"paragraph","text":"总理和张、焦二同志握手告别，张、焦二同志又走进双方汇报会议室。","index":35,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5f0f763dac","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}